verse
------------------------------------------
Network protocol for real-time sharing between graphical applications

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.2-1
  libssl1.1-1.1.1d-1
  libverse-devel-0.0.1-1bl1
  libverse0.1.0-0.0.1-1bl1
  libwslay0-1.1.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.0-1
  python27-2.7.16-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.14.5-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1
  python27-2.7.16-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/verse/verse

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/verse/verse/archive/v0.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack verse-0.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./verse-0.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/verse-0.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/verse-0.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libverse0.1.0-0.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libverse-devel-0.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/python2-verse-0.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(verse)
  /etc/verse/server.ini
  /etc/verse/users.csv
  /usr/bin/verse_server.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/verse.README
  /usr/share/doc/verse/README.md

(libverse0.1.0)
  /usr/bin/cygverse-0.1.0.dll

(libverse-devel)
  /usr/include/verse.h
  /usr/lib/libverse.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/verse.pc

(python2-verse)
  /usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/verse.dll

------------------

